WEBVTT

00:01.609 --> 00:03.414
Those monsters are on the loose,
we need to smoke them out.

00:03.974 --> 00:05.008
We'll start with the Hilltop.

00:05.744 --> 00:07.641
Previously on
"The Walking Dead"...

00:07.917 --> 00:10.675
Open up, ain't nobody leavin'
until they look around.

00:10.951 --> 00:13.813
You are gonna get me
my cash.

00:14.055 --> 00:18.227
They wanted us to stay quiet but
there are good people here.

00:18.503 --> 00:19.813
They need to know the truth.

00:20.089 --> 00:21.882
You want me to look
for secret files?

00:22.158 --> 00:24.468
Yes, and steal them.
This involves the Miltons?

00:24.744 --> 00:26.572
The young psychopath,
at least.

00:26.848 --> 00:30.227
My name is Lance Hornsby and I'm
here to offer you a job.

